\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T=\left(\frac{E_{s}}{p\beta c}\right)^{2}\frac{1}{X_{0}}
\]

\end_inset

light ion 对应的公式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T=\left(\frac{E_{s}}{p\beta c}\right)^{2}\frac{Z^{2}}{X_{0}}
\]

\end_inset


