 Interestingly enough,
 this value falls right between the suggested values in two similar studies:
 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{s}=17\,\mathrm{MeV}$
\end_inset

 [73] 和 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{s}=18.7\,\mathrm{MeV}$
\end_inset

[67]
